    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@vvo I am not sure if I understand it completely. \n\nWhen I talk about Refinement, I can only relate to RefinementList(dFR) and Menu(fR). \n\nEven if we keep the same name, there is a confusion in the way it accepts the props. \n\nNumericRefinement( string maybe ?), DisjunctiveFacetRefinement(array of items), FacetRefinement (string)\n\nAlso I would be pretty confused if hitsPerPage is renamed to default or current Refinement.  \n",
