    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "> I hesitated on this one indeed. If you come from a previous Algolia experience with instantsearch.js it will be seen as weird. If you are new to Algolia and only learning the connectors API, this should be a consistent experience with all the other connectors.\n\nMakes sense then. But then you have to change this all across plugins. I use python, java and javascript as well as instantsearch. \n",
